 via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-2236_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">In the UK, the Health and Social Care Act 2008 and guidelines from the Care Quality Commission (CQC) and the National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) underscore the importance of maintaining detailed and accurate patient records. Failure to comply can result in legal ramifications and impact care quality.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2238_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-2239_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-2240_">Guidelines for effective documentation
